0latticework%20alluding%20to%20the%20whorls%20of%20the%20rose%20flower%20that%20Nehru%20always%20wore%20in%20his%20lapel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20his%20father%2C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lies%20in%20architecting%20places%20that%20are%20rich%20with%20possibilities.%20His%20architectural%20vocabulary%20is%20angled%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimplistic%20design%20that%20aces%20functionality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20reasons%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20design%20needed%20to%20be%20simple%3B%20I%20wanted%20people%20to%20experience%20the%20forest%20and%20its%20views.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20the%20structure%20to%20be%20too%20intrusive%20within%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%20I%20agree%2C%20the%20walkway%20cuts%20through%20the%20forest%20with%20finesse%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20way%20of%20hope%20through%20the%20urban%20sprawl%20that%20skirts%20around%20its%20perimeter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20trees%20were%20cut%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%20The%20walkway%20has%20found%20its%20safe%20space%2C%20its%20Merbau%20wood%20torso%20supported%20by%20epoxy-coated%20steel%20columns%2C%20cradled%20by%20the%20land%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20huge%20hammock%20that%20finds%20support%20in%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20beams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20walk%20is%20punctuated%20by%20nameplates%20that%20bear%20mention%20of%20the%20different%20species%20of%20birds%20that%20call%20this%20forest%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebulbuls%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20par